@DATABASE "Shockway Rider"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Shockway Rider"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                              Shockway Rider
                              ==============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46119,183)"}         46119,183
@{"Infinite Lives+" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(46119,0)"}         46119,0
@{"Minutes = x    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43825,6)"}         43825,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Time  " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(57363,201)"}         57363,201
@{"Last Level     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(52340,0)"}         52340,0

                         Another one by me.

                         The "Infinite Lives+ POKE gives you Infinite Lives, plus
                         when you die, you complete the level. Pointless, but an
                         easy way of getting through the game :)

                         I currently have the "Minutes" POKE set to give you 6
                         minutes as that should be more than adequate. Plus, I
                         didn't want to set it to high because it takes AGES at
                         the end of level bonus counter.

                         Rastan.
@endnode
